text:
Look at that cake over there...!
It looks amazing...! So delicious...!

Shall we stop by the shop?
You can buy a cake.

W-Well then...
For Tenka, Naa-chan, and Chiyuki-san...

──N-No, it's... fine...!
We'll do it next time...!

What's wrong, Tenka...?
You don't have to hold back...

It's just... I thought maybe after
we finish working at the festival...

It would be nice for everyone to eat together...
As a way to say "thank you for your hard work"...!

Haha...
Yeah, that sounds good. Let's do that.

Hehe...
Yeah...! Looking forward to it...!
